name: AGs BACKROOMS Generator
description:
Prototype version of a VHS / PS1 / CRT style liminal Backrooms generator. Use Space Key to regenerate backrooms. LIMINAL: the quality of ambiguity or disorientation that occurs in the middle stage of a rite of passage, when participants no longer hold their pre-ritual status but have not yet begun the transition to the status they will hold when the rite is complete.
